headline: Iowans Keep Their Options Open
abstract: Ranking first is still the best, of course. But in the Iowa caucuses, second-choice candidates can win.
lead_paragraph: The snow was starting to come down. Senator Amy Klobuchar was snapping selfies at a campaign event. And Monica Peitz and Peg Raney, two friends from central Iowa, were discussing the question that it seemed every Democrat in the state was asking: Who is on your list?
